 from chmilar apple com michael chmilar subject re mbenz three zero zero series vw passat organization apple computer inc cupertino california lines three nine nntp posting host apple com jcorry erasure sl cc emory edu jeremy corry writes new three zero zero series mercedes benz wagon particularly i would like to hear about power manual t only any comparisons between the saab nine zero zero zero line and the mercedes would be helpful if a manual transmission is a must have then the m b three zero zero te is not in the running you cannot get a manual transmission in that car in north america it seems that buyers here or maybe more accurately the distributors are not interested in manual trannies the nine three three zero zero line comes with a two one seven hp engine all earlier years are one seven seven hp i have an eight seven three zero zero e with a mere one seven seven hp and auto tranny and i find that it has sufficient power for any normal driving situation more is always nice but i can t complain i test drove a saab nine zero zero cse last fall here are my impressions one awesome power especially over three five zero zero rpm when the turbo really comes on two if you get on the power really hard in a tight corner the front wheel drive causes it to understeer heavily and then viciously hook into the corner not a desirable handling trait but common in powerful front drive cars the cse is two zero zero hp mercedes is rear drive so it does not have this problem three huge interior and cargo space four the most rubbery shifter i have ever encountered i drove a five spd it was absolutely numb you might be able to get used to it i don t know i also didn t like its location which was too far down and too far right from the shifter s position i got the impression that saab really designed the car for an automatic five it was rather noisy engine buzz rattles and creaks mercedes does not exhibit these characteristics you should also check out the new bmw five two five touring this is a wagon version of the five two five i it fits into the class with the three zero zero te and saabs michael chmilar chmilar apple com